title: Eulima peracuta
text: Eulima peracuta is a <a href="species">species</a> of <a href="sea%20snail">sea snail</a>, a <a href="marine%20%28ocean%29">marine</a> <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a> in the <a href="family%20%28biology%29">family</a> <a href="Eulimidae">Eulimidae</a>. The species is one of a number within the genus "<a href="Eulima">Eulima</a>".
